  _releaseNote: "- \uAE30\uBCF8 BuildCommit workflow template\uC5D0 `CI_SECRET_ROOT=/Users/lydia/workspace/build-automation`\uC744
    \uBCF5\uAD6C\uD574 \uAE30\uC874 ActionFit runner\uC758 \uB85C\uCEEC credential
